     <div type="mnemonic_poem">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>A rule to know how many dayes be <hi>contained in euery moneth in</hi> the yeere.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>Thirty dayes hath Nouember,</l>
      <l>Aprill, Iune, and September.</l>
      <l>The rest hath thirty and one,</l>
      <l>Except it be February alone,</l>
      <l>Which alwayes hath twenty eight meere,</l>
      <l>When it is no Bisextile or Leape-yeere.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
